data.description: Beautiful home with plenty of great additions. Come enjoy this spacious 4 bedroom 3 bath centrally located new schools, shopping, hospitals, and more all within a couple minutes. Hardwood countertops with a breakfast bar perfect for entertaining. Nice large backyard perfect for Fido or entertaining & bonfires outside in the summer. Come take a look at this fantastic opportunity you won't be disappointed.
